THE CAUSE IS HUMANITY / Mort Sahl interviewed by Alan Farley. - Political satirist Mort Sahl is interviewed about show business personalities such as Bill Cosby, liberals, Gloria Steinem, Jim Garrison and the John F. Kennedy assassination, the spreading influence of the CIA, and the Pentagon's dominance of American society. - RECORDED: San Francisco Playboy Club. BROADCAST: KPFA, 30 May 1970.